<div class="usa-modal usa-modal--lg" id="dm-editing-guide-modal" aria-labelledby="dm-editing-guide-modal-heading"
    aria-describedby="dm-editing-guide-modal-description">
    <div class="usa-modal__content">
        <div class="usa-modal__main">
            <section class="margin-bottom-3">
                <h2 class="usa-modal__heading" id="dm-editing-guide-modal-heading margin-bottom-3">
                    Editing guide
                </h2>
                <div class="usa-prose-body">
                    <p id="dm-editing-guide-modal-description">
                        Follow these instructions to build your innovation page. Your page is modular, meaning that
                        some sections in the editor are optional. You can choose to fill out only the sections that
                        make sense for your innovation. Required fields are denoted with an asterisk (*).
                    </p>
                </div>
            </section>
            <section class="">
                <h3 class="usa-prose-h4 margin-0">What you need</h3>
                <div>
                    <ul class="usa-prose-ul line-height-26 font-sans-md padding-left-1">
                        <li class="small-disc">To create a thorough page, you’ll be asked to
                            share data, images, video, instructions, files, and stories related to your
                            innovation.</li>
                        <li class="small-disc">All uploaded files should be displayed in a common file format
                            (.jpg, .jpeg, .png, or .pdf) that is ready to be shown to the public. Images must be
                            less than 32MB.</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </section>
            <section class="">
                <h3 class="usa-prose-h4 margin-0">Formatting and editing</h3>
                <div>
                    <ul class="usa-prose-ul line-height-26 font-sans-md padding-left-1">
                        <li class="small-disc">Please fill out all fields marked with an
                            asterisk(*). All other fields are optional.</li>
                        <li class="small-disc">Ensure your work is accurate, formatted
                            consistently, and as complete as possible before publishing.</li>
                        <li class="small-disc">Use sentence case (only capitalizing the first
                            word in titles) and spell out acronyms. Capitalize proper nouns and names.</li>
                        <li class="small-disc">You will be able to edit your innovation once
                            it’s published.</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </section>
            <section class="font-sans-md">
                <h3 class="usa-prose-h4 margin-0">Privacy policy</h3>
                <ul class="usa-prose-ul line-height-26 font-sans-md padding-left-1">
                    <li class="small-disc">Avoid entering Personally Identifiable
                        Information (PII) or Protected Health Information (PHI) for any individual, Veteran,
                        or patient.</li>
                    <li class="small-disc">If you post PII you must fill out and hold onto
                        <%= link_to 'VAF 10-3203', Constants::FORM_3203_URL, target: '_blank', class: 'usa-link usa-link--external' %>
                        and
                        <%= link_to 'VAF 10-5345', Constants::FORM_5345_URL, target: '_blank', class: 'usa-link usa-link--external' %>.
                    </li>
                    <li class="small-disc">
                        If you want to upload an image that features a Veteran, or text that includes a
                        Veteran's name or individually-identifiable information you must fill out and hold onto forms
                        <%= link_to 'VAF 10-3203', Constants::FORM_3203_URL, target: '_blank', class: 'usa-link usa-link--external' %>
                        and
                        <%= link_to 'VAF 10-5345', Constants::FORM_5345_URL, target: '_blank', class: 'usa-link usa-link--external' %>.
                        Forms must be filled out with the 'External to VA' checkbox selected.
                    </li>
                    <li class="small-disc">
                        If you post PHI on the site you must fill out and hold onto
                        <%= link_to 'VAF 10-3203', Constants::FORM_3203_URL, target: '_blank', class: 'usa-link usa-link--external' %>
                        and
                        <%= link_to 'VAF 10-5345', Constants::FORM_5345_URL, target: '_blank', class: 'usa-link usa-link--external' %>.
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </section>
            <div class="usa-modal__footer">
                <div class="usa-summary-box editing-guide-help" role="region"
                    aria-labelledby="summary-box-key-information">
                    <div class="usa-summary-box__body">
                        <h3 class="usa-summary-box__heading" id="summary-box-key-information">
                            Need help?
                        </h3>
                        <div class="usa-summary-box__text">
                            <p> If you need additional help, email a member of our team with any questions at <a
                                    class="usa-link" href="mailto:marketplace@va.gov">marketplace@va.gov</a>.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <button class="usa-button usa-modal__close dm-editing-guide-modal-close" aria-label="Close this window"
            data-close-modal>
            <i class="fas fa-times"></i>
        </button>
    </div>
</div>